          <title>
            <string language="en">Infra-red and ultraviolet waves</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Infrarot- und Ultravioletwellen</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Vagues infrarouges et d'ultra-violet</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ondas infravermelhas e da ultravioleta</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Onde di ultraviolet ed infrarosse</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Υπέρυθρες ακτίνες και υπεριώδη κύματα</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ondas infrarrojas y del ultravioleta</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This experimental set-up proves that there are waves outside the spectrum that can't be seen. Some of these waves are infra-red and ultraviolet waves.</string>
          </description>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese experimentelle Installation prüft, daß es
Wellen außerhalb des Spektrums gibt, das nicht gesehen werden kann. 
Einige dieser Wellen sind Infrarot- und Ultravioletwellen.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette installation expérimentale montre qu'il y 
a des vagues en dehors du spectre qui ne peut pas être vu. 
Certaines de ces vagues sont les vagues infrarouges et 
d'ultra-violet.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta instalação experimental prova que há 
ondas fora do spectrum que não pode ser visto. Algumas destas 
ondas são ondas infravermelhas e da ultravioleta.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa messa a punto sperimentale dimostra che ci
sono onde fuori dello spettro che non può essere visto. Alcune 
di queste onde sono onde di ultraviolet ed infrarosse.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η πειραματική οργάνωση αποδεικνύει ότι υπάρχουν
κύματα έξω από το φάσμα που δεν μπορεί να δει. 
Μερικός από αυτά τα κύματα είναι υπέρυθρα και υπεριώδη 
κύματα.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta disposición experimental prueba que hay 
ondas fuera del espectro que no puede ser considerado. Algunas 
de estas ondas son ondas infrarrojas y del ultravioleta.</string>
          </description>
